{"categories":["beauty-cosmetics","teaser","mystery-email","fashion"],"collections":"","description":"Unveil your latest beauty and cosmetics range with our exclusive email template designed to captivate and enthrall. Perfectly tailored for product launches and teaser campaigns, this template announces your newest creations with a touch of mystery and fashion flair. Whether you're introducing a revolutionary wellness range or a game-changing cosmetic line, this invitation will pique curiosity and build anticipation. With a blend of elegance and intrigue, your audience will be eagerly awaiting the grand reveal of your new products. Turn every product launch into a must-attend event with this stylish and engaging email template.","short_description":"Introduce your latest beauty and cosmetics range with our exclusive email template. Ideal for product launches and teaser campaigns, it builds anticipation with a blend of mystery and fashion. Perfect for new wellness or cosmetic lines, it turns every launch into a must-attend event.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/jen-schmaltz.jpg","description":"Graphic Design is at the heart of my story, but I’ve been known to write myself a new part now and again… happily and frequently embracing such roles as: Project Manager, Strategic Thinker, Visual Communicator, Copy Writer, Brand Stylist and Content Curator... magician.\r\n\r\nDesign is where my passion and my purpose intersect, and providing clients with “the goods” to help their businesses soar is a pretty amazing thing to hop outta’ bed and do each day!","short_description":"","display_name":"Jen Schmaltz","id":"jen-schmaltz"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"><!--[if m